spec_data.Name: texlive-pst-eps
spec_data.Description:
Pst-eps is a PSTricks-based package for exporting PSTricks
images 'on the fly' to encapsulated PostScript (EPS) image
files, which can then be read into a document in the usual way.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:12:52 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Create EPS files from PSTricks figures
